SUMMARY:Spring Craft Faire
DESCRIPTION:Elks Club Spring Craft Faire \nJoin us for a fun day of shopping\, food\, and springtime cheer! \nFree Admission\nDelicious Breakfast & Lunch by Sax’s Joint\nShop unique gifts perfect for:\n• Mother’s Day\n• Father’s Day\n• Easter\n• Graduation \nBrowse a wonderful selection of handmade goods\, creative treasures\, and one-of-a-kind finds from talented local vendors. \nBring a friend and come support small businesses — we can’t wait to see you there!
