SUMMARY:Hardly Strictly Irish at The Wild Poppy Cafe!
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy live music by Hardly Strictly Irish and delectable food at this popular cafe on its gorgeous\, creekside patio! \nHARDLY STRICTLY IRISH (Suzuki Cady & Jimmy Murphy) play lovely\, lively traditional Irish tunes and sing soulful songs from a variety of genres on fiddle\, mandolin\, guitar\, and bodhrán. \n“A new\, local band is rocking the Bay Area—to high acclaim…They are commensurate acoustic musicians with decades of experience between them.” – Mark Fernquest\, Sebastopol Times
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/hardly-strictly-irish-at-the-wild-poppy-cafe/
LOCATION:Wild Poppy\, 9890 Bodega Highway\, Sebastopol\, CA\, 95472\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music
END:VEVENT
