SUMMARY:Jazz in the Plaza
DESCRIPTION:Every Sunday: Free\, live jazz every week performed by some of the best musicians in the SF Bay Area and beyond\, right in the heart of downtown Petaluma! Every Sunday from 1 to 3:30\, local jazz bassist\, music book publisher\, and KRCB host Chuck Sher presents a rotating ensemble of professional\, veteran jazz musicians in Putnam Plaza Park\, right next to the Speakeasy. This event started in 2020 and has since become a staple for locals and visitors alike. Stop by and enjoy some of the best jazz the Bay Area has to offer!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/jazz-in-the-plaza-20/
LOCATION:Putnam Plaza\, 129 Petaluma Blvd N\, Petaluma\, CA
