SUMMARY:Smoke N Mirrors at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Sunday Social at the Roadhouse! \nSmoke N Mirrors is a 5-piece live performance band based in Sonoma County / Santa Rosa\, California. They’re known locally for energetic live sets covering a broad range of classic and danceable music spanning multiple genres — including rock\, doo-wop\, R&B\, country\, and folk — with tight harmonies and crowd-pleasing arrangements.They play rock ’n’ roll and classic hits\, often focusing on covers from the 50s through the 80s\, with influences ranging from The Beatles and Eagles to CCR and Otis Redding.The band’s repertoire also includes doo-wop\, country\, folk\, and R&B standards performed with a spirited twist.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/smoke-n-mirrors-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
LOCATION:Rio Nido Roadhouse\, 14540 Canyon 2 Road\, Rio Nido\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.5205;-122.979
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Rio Nido Roadhouse 14540 Canyon 2 Road Rio Nido CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=14540 Canyon 2 Road:geo:-122.979,38.5205
END:VEVENT
