SUMMARY:Jeffrey Halford at Redwood Cafe
DESCRIPTION:Jeffrey Halford is a rock & roll lifer\, a Texas-born\, California-bred traditionalist trading in Americana mythologies. His solo album\, West Toward South\, serves them up not repurposed so much as distilled\, harking back to a time when outlaws had more style and panache than today’s suits. “A Town Called Slow” begins things in medias res:
