SUMMARY:Sonoma County Painting for Endometriosis
DESCRIPTION:About the Event \nGrab your friends for an unforgettable night for a fantastic cause. Held at Hopmonk tavern in Sebastopol\, CA\, this event will be two-fold: \nPaint Night \nYour reservation\nAll of your painting supplies\n1 Beverage Ticket\nDine & Donate \n20% of all food sales will be donated to AEEP (if you show them a flyer)\nSo\, come paint with us and have a great time! If you have other family members or friends who are not coming to Paint Night\, invite them to Dine and Donate. Endometriosis affects everyone in some way\, so let’s all be a part of the solution. Join us March 8 at 6:00 at Hopmonk in Sebastopol for a great time and to make a great impact.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/sonoma-county-painting-for-endometriosis/
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern – Sebastopol\, 230 Petaluma Ave\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Other
GEO:38.4012;-122.823
